sentences.english: Only the fiercest fighters of Mindanao could not be conquered.

sentences.english: The bomb went off in Cotabato city on the southern island of Mindanao.

sentences.english: Al Jacinto is a Mindanao publisher and political analyst.

sentences.english: A member of any of several peoples of the mountains of northern Luzon in the Philippines.

sentences.english: The Indonesian town of Medan also held a demonstration against the film.
